    "body": "> @hesterbruikman @errorists do we understand how iOS/Android decide to hide the top bar?\r\n\r\nTo add, here are 2 related issues. If we solve them, it'll probably make it easier to fix this. I don't think we control the topbar well atm.\r\n\r\n- Include a safeArea in the topbar: https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/8981\r\n- Search bar hide on scroll (address bar would than act as the Search bar component: https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/7697\r\n\r\nThe browser address bar is currently out of scope for #8981 I'm not sure why that is though. Probably @rachelhamlin or @flexsurfer can answer that.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
